# --- 构建产物 ---
# 主二进制 (go build -o dnsforvpn ./cmd/dnsforvpn/)
/dnsforvpn
# make <os> 输出目录 (build/linux, build/windows, build/macos, build/openwrt)
/build/
# vite 构建输出 (main 通过 frontend/embed.go 内嵌; 保留占位 index.html 使裸克隆可编译)
frontend/dist/*
!frontend/dist/index.html

# --- 前端依赖 ---
frontend/node_modules/

# --- 运行时数据 ---
# BoltDB 缓存库 (configs/data/dns_cache.db, 含缓存与自定义 DNS) — 运行时生成
configs/data/
# GFWList 种子文件 configs/rules/gfwlist.txt 随仓库/安装包携带, 不再忽略

# --- Go ---
*.exe
*.test
*.out

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
